data.description: This is the one, convenience is an understatement! This centrally located condo showcases 2 oversized bedrooms, 1 bathroom & is on the ground floor allowing for a seamless flow to its relaxing back patio & yard. Surrounded by trees & greenery it provides the perfect place for a morning cup of coffee, entertaining, BBQ’s, or simply relaxing! Move right in to many updates; beautiful vinyl plank flooring, stainless steel appliances, high-quality W/D in unit, the list goes on! 1 reserved parking space & spacious storage. Plus, it is just blocks to the Light Rail station! Quick access to DT Seattle, SeaTac, Boeing all via Light Rail. Choose from many popular dining & shopping options all around – Welcome Home!
